Package eu.sternbauer.EtlGenerator.Generation.internal.model

Class SimpleTable

java.lang.Object
eu.sternbauer.EtlGenerator.Generation.internal.model.SimpleTable
public class SimpleTable extends Object
A minimal subset of all required elements needed from the table elements. As the shortname are only set after the elements are created and Java records to not support mutable fields, this is not a record class.
